This is a native bare-swift package; it is not derived from any upstream
Rust crate. The encoder implements the OpenTelemetry OTLP/logs wire
format from `opentelemetry/proto/logs/v1/logs.proto` directly, and
re-uses the OTLP common types (`Resource`, `KeyValue`, `AnyValue`,
`InstrumentationScope`) from swift-otlp-exporter.

OpenTelemetry: https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-proto
Apache 2.0; see https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-proto/blob/main/LICENSE.
